{"Id":490439,"Title":"凝道之什","Dynasty":"明","Author":"湛若水","Context":"坎坎击鼓，于樵之巅。乃荐乃献，尹公之贤。于贤维何，德义迁迁。坎坎击鼓，烟霞之下。乃咏乃歌，饯尹公者。于咏维何，德音雅雅。亦既击鼓，亦既考钟。以宴以乐，公坐于宫。维公在宫，威仪颙颙。击鼓喤喤，考钟锵锵。以乐以宴，公坐于堂。维公在堂，德容不忘。维钟维鼓，维瑟维琴。何以假之，嗣此德音。维此德音，维樵之岑。维琴维瑟，维钟维鼓。维以足蹈，维以手舞。其乐未央，公晏灵府。作乐歌舞，出饯尹公。声影悬矣，送之九龙。九龙跃跃，导之以樵风。谁其主之，兀厓来同。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"e17193f260ddf9f21a942b629609ef44","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6562512,"Sentence":"坎坎击鼓，于樵之巅。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"kǎn kǎn jī gǔ ，yú qiáo zhī diān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6562513,"Sentence":"乃荐乃献，尹公之贤。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"nǎi jiàn nǎi suō ，yin gōng zhī xián ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6562514,"Sentence":"于贤维何，德义迁迁。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yú xián wéi hé ，dé yǐ qiān qiān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6562515,"Sentence":"坎坎击鼓，烟霞之下。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"kǎn kǎn jī gǔ ，yān xiá zhī xià ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6562516,"Sentence":"乃咏乃歌，饯尹公者。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"nǎi yǒng nǎi gē ，jiàn yin gōng zhě ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6562517,"Sentence":"于咏维何，德音雅雅。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yú yǒng wéi hé ，dé yīn yā yā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6562518,"Sentence":"亦既击鼓，亦既考钟。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yì jì jī gǔ ，yì jì kǎo zhōng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6562519,"Sentence":"以宴以乐，公坐于宫。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yi yàn yi lè ，gōng zuò yú gōng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6562520,"Sentence":"维公在宫，威仪颙颙。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wéi gōng zài gōng ，wēi yǐ yóng yóng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English